{"tid":1517721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「置頂」請不要怪責民陣。香港人互相合作登頂。","createTime":"2019-08-30T04:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T13:06:23.000Z","uid":8948,"like":219,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"f2dc110650c1510ebed19a3bc6b47fc932b56eca","tid":1517721,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:08:07.000Z","msg":"民陣係唯一一個團體可以號召所有和理非上街<br />\n請大家明白佢今次取消遊行既決定係為左保住呢塊「合法遊行」既金漆招牌，令佢地往後可以繼續用呢塊招牌去號召民眾。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地所有文宣既方向應該係</span><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n<br />\n1。連合法和理非上街都被禁止，另類戒嚴已經降臨香港－＞spin 去戒嚴，罷買，跳閘等行動。<br />\n2。連和理非上街都唔俾，白色恐怖已經係你身上－＞spin 去繼續自發上街，10點鳩叫等行動。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>兄弟爬山，不分化，不割蓆，不捉鬼，齊上齊落！和勇合一，光復香港，時代革命。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"bafe63794e13c390fd36f16537c563095b1c8936","tid":1517721,"uid":8948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:08:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81bfd7bedd72e1ad24786fea823c88026131ef1a","tid":1517721,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T04:08:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8kYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=c74e0dce\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8kYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=ae4e5862\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuck